this conversation,

01:02:25.140 --> 01:02:26.960 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to would push it
to the next conversation,

01:02:26.960 --> 01:02:28.310 align:middle line:90%
and pick it up there, OK?

01:02:28.310 --> 01:02:28.880 align:middle line:90%
>>HOROWITZ: Sounds great.

01:02:28.880 --> 01:02:30.213 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK, it's been a blast.

